MANGADualist is a fork of the famous TLK Powermanga 2D shoot-em-up game.

Major changes:

	* Requires SDL2.

ToDo:

	* Add dual player mode.

Notes:

	* The game play, graphics and music are not changed at all.
	* Some hardware support might be defunct (as i do not have handheld device for testing).

Fot the original game, please visit

	linux.tlk.fr/games/Powermanga

LEGAL

